msgid "Email Health Checks"
msgstr "E-post helsesjekk"

#: admin.php:13
msgid "Invalid interval. Use a number followed by m, h, or d — e.g. 1h, 30m, 2d."
msgstr "Ugyldig intervall. Bruk et tall etterfulgt av m, h eller d — f.eks. 1h, 30m, 2d."

#: admin.php:49
msgid "Sends a test email on a configurable schedule to confirm your outbound mail delivery is working. Designed for use with a healthchecks service, which alerts you if the expected ping stops arriving. Sending directly to your own inbox works too, if you are brave."
msgstr "Send en test-epost ut i fra en tidsplan for å sjekke at utgående e-postlevering fungerer. Laget for bruk med healthchecks. Sende direkte til egen innboks fungerer også, hvis du er modig."

